title: Factors Absorbing Reserve Funds: Deposits with Federal Reserve Banks, Other Than Reserve Balances: Service-Related: Adjustments to Compensate for Float (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
This item lists the adjustments to reserve balances made to compensate for float created through the direct participation of depository institutions in the interdistrict check-clearing process.

For more details, see http://www.federalreserve.gov/releases/h41/20120719/
